(10, 1, '2020-06-02 09:09:23', '2020-06-02 09:09:23', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We’ve seen some very cool 360º videos in the past, but this one ranks right up there with the best. It takes us to the Philippines where we dive under the water to explore an amazing reef system. But unlike most other 360º videos where the ability to pan around and look in all directions is used as a gimmick to lure viewers in, there is actually a story to be told here. This preview of&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.vaninaharel.com/grandpasreef\">a much larger and longer video experience</a>&nbsp;shares the story of a young girl who took up her grandfather’s cause to protect this reef. Because of their efforts, it is doing much better than many similar reefs in the area, which serves as an inspiration for the rest of us to do our part as well.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Video: Exploring ‘Grandpa’s Reef’ in 360º Video', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '1-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-06-02 09:09:23', '2020-06-02 09:09:23', '', 1, 'http://localhost/wordpress/2020/06/02/1-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
