he reader surmount life’s difficulties:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Identifying the Obstacles in Your Life</li><li>Getting Out of Your Own Way</li><li>Finding Success</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Featuring practical advice, inspirational quotes, engaging stories, and interesting anecdotes, <em>Overcoming Obstacles</em> will give readers the tools they need to triumph in the face of adversity.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><em>Facing Your Fears: A Navy SEAL’s Guide to Coping With Fear and Anxiety</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/adventureblog.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/facing-your-fears.jpg?w=300&amp;ssl=1\" alt=\"\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Facing-Your-Fears-Conquering-Doubts/dp/1510745742/\">Buy at Amazon.com</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Wisdom and Inspiration to Help You Overcome Your Doubts from a&nbsp;<em>New York Times</em>&nbsp;Bestselling Author</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A former Navy SEAL and current motivational speaker, Don Mann specializes in helping others achieve success in every aspect of life—personal and professional—by using techniques employed by Navy SEALs. In&nbsp;<em>Facing Your Fears,</em>&nbsp;Mann zeroes in on finding ways to cope with the fear and anxieties readers face in their lives, no matter what they may be. This volume includes three subsections dedicated to helping the reader cope with his or her doubts and worries:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Identifying Your Fears</li><li>Embracing the Fear</li><li>Letting Go of the Fear</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Featuring practical advice, inspirational quotes, engaging stories, and interesting anecdotes, <em>Facing Your Fears</em> will give readers the tools they need to triumph in the face of adversity.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><em>Choosing Your Battles: Inspiration and Wisdom from a Navy SEAL on How to Win Your Battles and Ensure a Positive Outcome</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img src=\"https://i2.wp.com/adventureblog.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/choosing-your-battles.jpg?w=300&amp;ssl=1\" alt=\"\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Choosing-Your-Battles-Inspiration-Positive/dp/1510752048\">Preorder on Amazon.com</a> (Coming July 7, 2020)</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Wisdom and Inspiration to Help You Overcome Your Doubts from a&nbsp;<em>New York Times</em>&nbsp;Bestselling Author</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A former Navy SEAL and current motivational speaker, Don Mann specializes in helping others achieve success in every aspect of life—personal and professional—by using techniques employed by Navy SEALs. In&nbsp;<em>Choosing Your Battles,</em>&nbsp;Mann zeroes in on finding ways to choose which battles are worth fighting, no matter what they may be. This volume includes three subsections dedicated to helping the reader cope with his or her doubts and worries:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Drawing a Line in the Sand</li><li>Fight the Good Fight</li><li>Winning the Battle</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Featuring practical advice, inspirational quotes, engaging stories, and interesting anecdotes, <em>Choosing Your Battles</em> will give readers the tools they need to triumph in the face of adversity.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><em>Crimson Waters: Piracy Across the Ages</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/adventureblog.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/crimson-waters.jpg?w=300&amp;ssl=1\" alt=\"\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Crimson-Waters-Piracy-Across-Ages/dp/1510754873/\">Preorder on Amazon.com</a> (Coming September 8, 2020)</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>A&nbsp;<em>New York Times</em>&nbsp;bestsellling author separates history from myth from the Pharaohs to Blackbeard and Captain Kidd to today.&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Soon after the first maritime trade routes became operational, seafaring bandits appeared to prey upon the cargo, crews, and ships of others.&nbsp;<em>Crimson Waters&nbsp;</em>traces the history of piracy around the globe, stretching back from its roots in 2500 BCE, through the Golden Age of Piracy in the 17th and 18th centuries, and up to the modern-day pirates who still threaten boats along coastlines and on the open seas.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This journey through history includes:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Evidence of “Sea People” during the reigns of Egyptian Pharaohs</li><li>The raids and pillaging&nbsp;of seafaring Vikings</li><li>The tales of the Blackbeard, the Barbarossa Brothers, Calico Jack, Captain Kidd, Sir Francis Drake, and Madam Cheng</li><li>A historical account of the real pirates of the Caribbean</li><li>Pirates of the modern age and why the occupation has persevered</li><li>And more!</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>Crimson Waters</em> satisfies all the armchair swashbucklers who long for a sense of adventure and the history buffs looking to spruce up their knowledge of maritime exploits.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:social-links -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-social-links\"><!-- wp:social-link {\"url\":\"https://wordpress.org\",\"service\":\"wordpress\"} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:social-link {\"url\":\"d\",\"service\":\"facebook\"} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:social-link {\"url\":\"f\",\"service\":\"twitter\"} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:social-link {\"url\":\"d\",\"service\":\"instagram\"} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:social-link {\"url\":\"f\",\"service\":\"linkedin\"} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:social-link {\"url\":\"d\",\"service\":\"youtube\"} /--></ul>\n<!-- /wp:social-links -->', 'MY BOOKS', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '67-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-06-02 18:36:23', '2020-06-02 18:36:23', '', 67, 'http://localhost/wordpress/2020/06/02/67-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
